Convert to list/data.frame

Source: R/data_frame.R
data_frame.Rd

Convert to list/data.frame

Usage

as_list(x, ...)

as_data_frame(x, ...)

Arguments

x

ccn object

...

additional arguments

Value

list or data.frame

Examples

as_list(decode("670055"))
#> $category
#> [1] "Medicare Provider"
#> 
#> $number
#> [1] "670055"
#> 
#> $seq_number
#> [1] "0055"
#> 
#> $seq_range
#> [1] "0001-0879"
#> 
#> $seq_abbr
#> [1] "ACUTE"
#> 
#> $seq_desc
#> [1] "Short-Term Hospital (General & Specialty)"
#> 
#> $state_code
#> [1] "67"
#> 
#> $state_abbr
#> [1] "TX"
#> 
#> $state_name
#> [1] "Texas"
#> 
#> $type_code
#> [1] NA
#> 
#> $type_abbr
#> [1] NA
#> 
#> $type_desc
#> [1] NA
#> 
#> $parent_code
#> [1] NA
